      <title>GitHub代理失效</title>
      <link href="/2023/08/24/GitHub%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88/"/>
      <url>/2023/08/24/GitHub%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="GitHub执行命令失败"><a href="#GitHub执行命令失败" class="headerlink" title="GitHub执行命令失败"></a>GitHub执行命令失败</h1><p><strong>错误代码</strong>  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Failed to connect to github.com port 443</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="本地已经启动了VPN"><a href="#本地已经启动了VPN" class="headerlink" title="本地已经启动了VPN"></a>本地已经启动了VPN</h2><p>网页可以打开github。说明命令行在拉取&#x2F;推送代码时并没有使用vpn进行代理<br>说明VPN配置，并没有生效，需要单独给git配置代理</p><h3 id="socks5"><a href="#socks5" class="headerlink" title="socks5"></a>socks5</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy socks5 127.0.0.1:7890</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy socks5 127.0.0.1:7890</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="http-实测有效"><a href="#http-实测有效" class="headerlink" title="http(实测有效)"></a><strong>http</strong>(实测有效)</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 如果是 socks5</span><br><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy 127.0.0.1:7890</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy 127.0.0.1:7890</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/luokine/blogimage/master/img/20230824152505.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
